items.name: Saul Goodman from "Breaking Bad/Better call Saul" (2008-2022)
items.description:
After 122 models, 498 hours of processing, 2800 likes and 21K downloads, I want to sincerely thank the 7 people in total who supported me to make those models.

The model removed by Civitai will be reposted with prude CIVITAI standart showcase.

James Morgan "Jimmy" McGill, better known by his business name Saul Goodman, is a character created by Vince Gilligan and Peter Gould and portrayed by Bob Odenkirk in the television franchise Breaking Bad. He appears as a major character in Breaking Bad (2008–2013) and as the titular antihero protagonist of its spin-off Better Call Saul (2015–2022).

Saul is a self-centered and unscrupulous Albuquerque-based lawyer who embraces his tactics as a former scam artist and becomes involved in the city's criminal underworld. In Breaking Bad, he acts as the consigliere for the methamphetamine cooks Walter White (Bryan Cranston) and Jesse Pinkman (Aaron Paul) and plays a crucial role in the development of their drug empire. Better Call Saul's main prequel storyline depicts Saul's origins as the earnest lawyer Jimmy McGill and his moral deterioration in the six years before the events of Breaking Bad; it also features a sequel storyline, where Saul is living under the assumed name Gene Takavic, that explores the consequences of his actions in Breaking Bad.

This model is trained with SFW sources only. If you get NSFW content, you did it in purpose, didn't you?

Please provide constructive criticism.

You can support me here to be able to render better models (https://ko-fi.com/djo226). Supporters can request model.

Prompt : Saul, photography, trending on artstation, sharp focus, studio photo, intricate details, highly detailed, by greg rutkowski <lora:Saul:0.8>

Negative prompt: (deformed iris, deformed pupils, semi-realistic, cgi, 3d, render, sketch, cartoon, drawing, anime, mutated hands and fingers:1.4), (deformed, distorted, disfigured:1.3), poorly drawn, bad anatomy, wrong anatomy, extra limb, missing limb, floating limbs, disconnected limbs, mutation, mutated, ugly, disgusting, amputation

Steps: 70, Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras, CFG scale: 7, Seed: -1, Face restoration: GFPGAN, Size: 768x768, Model hash: 81086e2b3f, Model: realisticVisionV20_v20

Face restoration is optional, may provide better result if not activated.

Use Saul as trigger.

Important:

This Lora model is a virtual representation of a natural person and it is important to emphasize that its use must not be illegal or degrading. I want to remind you that any infringement in this regard is the responsibility of the user and not that of the designer of this model.

It is crucial to respect laws and ethical standards regarding the use of this technology. Any abusive or illegal use of this model is strictly prohibited and could result in legal consequences for the user.

As the designer of this model, I take the responsibility of ensuring that it is used in an ethical and responsible manner very seriously. I rely on each user to do the same and to act in compliance with the laws and ethical standards in force.

items.name: Bianca - Hentai University
items.description:
This is a LoRA for the character Bianca, from Hentai University a game by Noodle Jacuzzi.

Bianca's art is from the artist Oreteki18kin, the set -

Haramitai! Natsu Nakadashi Kyouka Gasshuku

I've been working my way through making these for all the characters currently in the game, and sharing them in the Discord for HU, but figured I should also put them up here.

In general, I'm working from pretty limited image sets, so expect the results to be a bit wonky at times. These (and the rest of the gym girls) especially only have about 15 images to work from each, and they're not ideal images. It still works, but it takes more finagling that some of the other characters for sure.

I recommend a weight of around 0.5, possibly lower depending if you're combining the character LoRA with other styles/costumes/etc. along with tagging some defining characteristics of the character you're generating. Higher than that can really push the artist's original style, and may cause you issues.

All characters I train have a "character tag" added into the set to help generate them fairly reliably.

Recommended LoRA Weight - 0.5 for fairly flexible, higher if you want more of the original artist's style, lower if it doesn't play nice with other loras.

Character tag - HUBianca
Recommended tags - light brown hair, green eyes, short hair, hair ribbon, curvy, huge breasts,

I may have forgotten to check and tag eye color when doing my testing, but hey. If you want it to be "set accurate" be sure to tag.

I've got quite a backlog of these made up already, so I'll be uploading them on and off.

Check my other uploads as I put them out for more HU characters, and if you want any specific character put up soon, let me know.

items.name: Harry Callahan from "Dirty Harry" (1971)
items.description:
After 123 models, 502 hours of processing, 2900 likes and 21K downloads, I want to sincerely thank the 7 people in total who supported me to make those models.

The model removed by Civitai will be reposted with prude CIVITAI standart showcase.

Inspector Harold Francis Callahan (born October 24, 1928), nicknamed Dirty Harry, is a fictional character and protagonist of the Dirty Harry film series, which consists of Dirty Harry (1971), Magnum Force (1973), The Enforcer (1976), Sudden Impact (1983), and The Dead Pool (1988). Callahan is portrayed by Clint Eastwood in each film.

From his debut, Callahan became the template for a new kind of film cop: an antihero who does not hesitate to cross professional boundaries in pursuit of his own vision of justice, especially when the law is poorly served by an inept, incompetent bureaucracy.

All of the Dirty Harry films feature Callahan killing criminals, mostly in gunfights. Phrases he utters in armed stand-offs, "Go ahead, make my day" and "[...] you've got to ask yourself one question: 'Do I feel lucky?' Well, do ya, punk?" have become iconic. As the 1971 film was criticized for carrying "authoritarian" undertones, the sequels attempted to be more balanced by pitting Harry against villains from a broader ideological spectrum, notably in 1973's Magnum Force, in which Harry is shown fighting vigilantism after it goes too far.

This model is trained with SFW sources only. If you get NSFW content, you did it in purpose, didn't you?

If you want to support me buy me a coffee!

Triggerwords: None.

Notes:

  • Sometimes produces closeups when not prompted, just put close-up in the negative prompt.

  • The backgrounds tend to work out better when generating pictures in landscape/horizontal resolutions rather than portrait/vertical ones.

  • It will sometimes ignore solo/1girl/1boy and proceed to create a landscape-shot, just add no humans to the negative prompt.

  • Prompting from behind will make the LoRA almost always focus on the subject's butt for better or for worse. To prevent this just put ass focus and/or ass in the negative prompt.

items.name: Octopus
items.description:
LoRA trained to generate octopus. It can also generate NSFW.

The dataset wasn't ideal to generalize and maintain consistency, so not all gens will be good and may require tweaking your prompt or changing seed. I may revisit it if there's enough interest for an update.

Please rate and leave a like if you enjoyed it! And be sure to follow to check out the upcoming models.

Trigger: octopus

Other useful tags to combine with: animal, tentacles, cephalopod eyes.

Additional info

I make these models for fun and for the challenge and release them for free for everyone to enjoy, for non-commercial use (see license). The one thing I ask of you is to provide rating and feedback! That helps me understand where I can improve and helps me stay motivated to produce more content!

I accept suggestions or requests here or on Civitai discord server.

You can also check my more polished images and upcoming models on my pixiv profile.

items.name: CloudFantsy (云中幻梦)
items.description:
Model Introduction:

Amidst the vast expanse of time, white clouds drift leisurely, as the azure sky forms an unobstructed canopy. Welcome to CloudFantasy, the seventh installment of my Texture Sensations series. This model presents a breathtaking experience of strolling through the clouds, immersing you in a dreamlike journey through the sky. Drawing inspiration from various cloud types, CloudFantasy meticulously crafts scenes that allow you to savor the soft and elegant beauty of cloud textures.

Generation suggestions:

Recommended Weights: 1

Models: Applicable to various base models; all example images are produced from different base models.

Primary Trigger Word (non-essential): clouds

Secondary Trigger Words (each may yield different effects, select as needed):

alt clouds #(altocumulus clouds)

asp clouds #(asperatus clouds)

billow clouds #(billowing cumulus clouds)

cir clouds #(cirrus clouds)

cumu clouds #(cumulus clouds)

lent clouds #(lenticular clouds)

mam clouds #(mammatus clouds)

nimbo clouds #(nimbostratus clouds)

Recommended Basic PROMPT: ((masterpiece)), ((best quality)), 8k, high detailed, ultra-detailed, 1girl, full body, outdoors, clouds

模型简介：白云千载空悠悠，青天一片无遮凝。质感系列第七弹，CloudFantsy (云中幻梦)模型将为您呈现一个令人惊叹的云端漫步体验，感受如梦似幻的空中旅程。本模型取材自各种类型的云，经过精心调制，让您可以在不同的场景中品味云层的绵柔的质感和优雅的美丽。

推荐权重：1

推荐模型：适用于各种类型的底模，所有例图均由不同底模产出。

基础触发词（非必要）：clouds

次级触发词（每种可能会有不同的效果，按需选择）：

alt clouds #高积云
